text: Rune Andersson (28 April 1919 - 27 August 1992) was a Swedish sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1919 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Swedish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sweden Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Västra Götaland County
